### Shop Cart API Test Requests

### 1. Create a new cart
POST https://localhost:7001/api/v1/carts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "country": "GB"
}

### 2. Get all products
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/products

### 3. Get a specific product
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/products/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

### 4. Add multiple items to cart (replace {cart-id} with actual cart ID)
POST https://localhost:7001/api/v1/carts/{cart-id}/items/batch
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
      "quantity": 1
    },
    {
      "productId": "44444444-4444-4444-4444-444444444444",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

### 5. Apply discount code
POST https://localhost:7001/api/v1/carts/{cart-id}/discount-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SAVE10"
}

### 6. Get cart totals
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/carts/{cart-id}/totals

### 7. Get cart details
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/carts/{cart-id}

### 8. Health check
GET https://localhost:7001/api/v1/health

